  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You&rsquo;ve had all too much practice at close-in fighting and desperate struggles with pistol or blade. You&rsquo;re extremely skilled at avoiding injury in melee combat, and at level 2 you can dodge through a melee scrum without fear of being knifed in passing.</p><p><strong>Level 1:</strong> Gain any combat skill as a bonus skill. You can use pistol-sized ranged weapons in melee without suffering penalties for the proximity of melee attackers. You ignore Shock damage from melee assailants, even if you&rsquo;re unarmored at the time.</p><p><strong>Level 2:</strong> The Shock damage from your melee attacks treats all targets as if they were AC 10. The Fighting Withdrawal combat action is treated as an On Turn action for you and can be performed freely.</p>",
